 On Saturday, the 14th of September, in Brooklyn, New York, American singer, Chris Brown brought out Nigerian pop singer, Davido to perform with him at the Barclays Centre during his Indigo Tour. The video which was posted on Instagram saw Davido and Chris Brown performing IF together and then going on to perform their hit collabo, Blow My Mind. Davido had revealed in an interview with Ebro Darden that Chris Brown will be taking him on his Indigo tour.  The tour which will come to an end on the 19th of October still has over twenty stops in the United State and we do not know if Davido will performing in all those locations. Watch videos:   #ChrisBrown and #Davido performing #IF at his #NewYork stop of his #indigotour #afrobeats #music #BlowMyMind #Notjustok A post shared by  Notjustok.com (@notjustok) on Sep 15, 2019 at 12:29am PDT //www.instagram.com/embed.js   #Davido and #ChrisBrown performing #BlowMyMind at the #barclayscenter in #Newyork  #afrobeats #music #Notjustok A post shared by  Notjustok.com (@notjustok) on Sep 15, 2019 at 12:36am PDT //www.instagram.com/embed.js The post Chris Brown Brings Out Davido At The New York Stop Of His Indigo Tour | Watch Video appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: NotJust okay